com.avanza.astrix.provider.core

Annotation Type Library


  • @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
public @interface Library
    Used to publish a library as part of an api, see AstrixApiProvider for more information. The method holding this annotation will be used as a factory to create an instance of the given type at runtime.

    Author:
    Elias Lindholm (elilin)
